{"tid":1318733,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(小建議）撤退方法","createTime":"2019-07-15T04:10:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T13:00:41.000Z","uid":268690,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"382608a45191e8d13921eb798debcdd57e95890e","tid":1318733,"uid":268690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T04:10:04.000Z","msg":"見之前po過，無乜人應，唯有改下再出。<br />\n其實勇武派每次開始就一定行頭，撤就一定行最後。<br />\n既然係咁，勇武派有無諗過做多少少將我方傷害減至最少？<br />\n小建議，例如撤退個陣，即警犬進攻個陣，警犬會喺我地後方，勇武派可利用警犬鐘意仆街特性，撤退時向後倒油喺地下（唔好買合興旗下油），或者用其他可緩減犬隻速度的物品，例如彈珠、波子等。起馬俾到間多時間老嫩撤退。"},{"pid":"cf8e9a08f0a5de8c07f1e0bbae81901f906deeff","tid":1318733,"uid":268690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T04:14:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d2abc1481f22e618c819f05b99ce4977b6b2ef1b","tid":1318733,"uid":268690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T04:16:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"13904d11dee114c96dcee0ef6ee4b1950883b5cf","tid":1318733,"uid":268690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T04:20:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"347de117f15cd1ae042a158d8ae6e7cdc7907b06","tid":1318733,"uid":268690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T04:50:41.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"697988b4dd11559ac8d41b7b8f7f5dc310db966e","tid":1318733,"uid":263192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T04:51:37.000Z","msg":"sorry打擾曬，借一借位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">[由今日起去到21號，就係最需要輿論戰既時候]</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1318740/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1318740/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"a64ac65eebc61613f95562ab0b600463ba9a62a5","tid":1318733,"uid":268690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T05:15:48.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e16f73fbbde029f26e3527459802df2d77f9c601","tid":1318733,"uid":268690,